# AI Around Me

## Objective
To identify real-life applications of Artificial Intelligence used daily.

## Applications

1. Netflix → Recommends shows using user behavior  
2. Google Maps → Predicts traffic using past data  
3. Instagram → Shows posts based on engagement  
4. Amazon → Suggests products using ML  
5. YouTube → Recommends videos  
6. Gmail → Filters spam emails  
7. Alexa/Siri → Voice recognition using NLP  
8. Google Photos → Face detection  
9. Uber → Predicts ride pricing  
10. Spotify → Music recommendations  

## Conclusion
AI is widely used in everyday life through recommendation systems, prediction models, and natural language processing.
